    "body": "I figured it out, partially. It seems that the new transactions were being added to the list of pending transactions with higher nonces. Therefore, they weren't being seen by the network. When I executed the transaction again with the correct nonce (in line with the live blockchain) it went through. I still don't know how to clear pending transactions, though. Is that possible?",
